@startuml 共享資料流（區塊鏈式）

title 共享資料流 - Hash 鏈與 Gossip 同步

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF

participant "Node A\n(SharedDataStream)" as A
participant "Node B\n(SharedDataStream)" as B
participant "Node C\n(SharedDataStream)" as C

note over A, C
  **LedgerEntry** = index, previousHash, payloadHash, timestamp, creatorId, payload, entryHash
  每筆 entryHash 依賴前一筆 → 形成 hash 鏈（不可竄改）
end note

A -> A : append(payload)\n→ previousHash = last.entryHash\n→ 計算 payloadHash, entryHash\n→ 寫入本地 entries[]

A -> B : Gossip(LedgerEntry)
A -> C : Gossip(LedgerEntry)

B -> B : handleReceivedEntry(entry)\n→ 驗證 entryHash\n→ 驗證 previousHash == 本地 last.entryHash\n→ 驗證 payloadHash\n→ append 到本地\n→ 通知監聽器

C -> C : handleReceivedEntry(entry)\n→ 同上

B -> A : (可選) 再轉發給其他鄰居
B -> C : (可選) 再轉發給其他鄰居

note over A, C
  **最終一致**：各節點維護同一條有序鏈，透過 Gossip 同步新條目
end note

@enduml
